Package edu.cnm.deepdive.worldofwardrobe.fragments

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccessoriesFragment
    AccessoriesFragment purpose is to show item type ID 5, 6, and 7 as defined in getItem(int position)
    BottomFragment
    BottomFragment purpose is to show item type ID 3 and 4 as defined in getItem(int position).
    EditFragment
    The edit fragment currently adding items with gallery intent and camera intent, add new wardrobe, and add new items type.
    ItemPicAdapter
    A custom array adapter to populates the layout with items from the item database.
    OutfitFragment
    The OutfitFragment display the one of each selected item type from the Top, Bottom, and Accessories Fragemtn to form an outfit.
    TopFragment
    This fragment purpose is to show item type ID 1 and 2 as defined in getItem(int position).
    WardrobeFragment
    this is the landing fragment page where clicking a wardrobe will only take the screen to the next fragment page, specified fron the OnClickListener.
    WardrobePicAdapter
    This Custom adapter is like the ItemPicAdapter except it has nothing to do with the OutfitFragment.
